trailingComments.value: * * Returns the last n elements of the input iterable in an array. * If n is negative, behaves like {@link drop}( iterable, * -n). * * @example * // returns [ 3 , 4 ] * list( tail( range( 5 ) , 2 ) ) ; * * @param {Iterable} iterable - The input iterable. * @param {Number} n - The number of elements to include in the output. * @returns {Array} - The last n elements of the input iterable.
